{"tid":719943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普限制「中資」態度軟化, 美股道瓊漲逾200點","createTime":"2018-06-27T16:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T01:18:39.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5606a32f54995d6349703e712c327a2b3f80e9","tid":719943,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"而家侵侵靠限制移民同travel ban都足以連任, 同習近平繼續做朋友都無問題. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2471282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2471282&d=8KvN3SaLyIZCNXzU7%2BCn%2BZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5615ed72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2471282&h=a1fedf4b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2471282</a><br />\n<br />\n川普限制中資態度軟化 美股道瓊漲逾200點<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-27 22:05<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕川普政府擬限制中國及其他外國資金對美國科技業的投資，傳出手段將不如先前預期的嚴苛，激勵美股3大指數週三開盤走高，道瓊工業指數更強漲逾200點。<br />\n<br />\n道瓊工業指數開盤上漲48點，早盤一度上漲逾200點，站上24500點關卡，開拓重工（Caterpillar）、波音（Boeing）、蘋果（Apple Inc.）股價皆相繼走高；科技股及能源類股上漲，帶動標普500指數上漲0.2％；那斯達克指數則上漲0.3％。<br />\n<br />\n為了防止美國科技技術被竊取，川普政府擬針對包含中國在內的外國投資施加限制，但傳出川普將採用的手段，並不如先前預期的，設下外國投資美國科技業比率不得超過25%的嚴格限制。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNBC》報導，有美國資深官員表示，川普政府將會透過新成立的美國外來投資委員會（CFIUS），來對可能竊取美國敏感科技技術的外來投資進行審查。這也使的市場對於貿易戰持續升溫的緊張情緒，也獲得些許緩解。"},{"pid":"8cb99709150f15c39ab694144eb6f418373ed122","tid":719943,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180627/1381053/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180627%2F1381053%2F&d=8KvN3SaLyIZCNXzU7%2BCn%2BZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ed835261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180627%2F1381053%2F&h=6f61cade\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180627/1381053/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普(Donald Trump)今表示，他支持加強管制美國敏感科技出口，嚴格限制外資投資美國科技業，但他並未針對中國而增加限制，《華爾街日報》解讀，川普放鬆（ease)對中國的限制，只是把現行法規變嚴格，由法規去管制。"},{"pid":"03d58d097491faf683511db94f0fc481675d4562","tid":719943,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e74bd7d3545d15aaf89261cb763e7ed52622cce","tid":719943,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"侵侵差不多所有野都選前交代哂<br />\n佢其實對中韓根本無實際野落過袋<br />\n點可能咁快完<br />\n侵要撐住<br />\n世界撥亂返正靠你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03168ec24260fe8efad24db35e33a85b6e20b5a","tid":719943,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"Trump 仔又放水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76860750f5a5ad8ece393d18d2a2c7b8210b1972","tid":719943,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<br />\n2025勢在必行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7a0e23fd15c52e1ae83d76570704af51e34d01","tid":719943,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:18:13.000Z","msg":"証明對抗中國的最大阻力就係美國人本身"},{"pid":"2ee18630e1e2723e8b6a4d92ba192dc828282e7d","tid":719943,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:01:42.000Z","msg":"已經有公司決定將生產線搬生，美國人唔駛返工，諗起都開心"},{"pid":"8138705e74237e0f64255b6c2e03bd1dd70d7167","tid":719943,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:02:18.000Z","msg":"呢d 帖無人敢面對？"},{"pid":"b45b41349cf143b7